Now after a hectic life, I wish to have time for myself and if I get a compatible life partner for him. I am very broadminded, courageous, strong willed and strong minded independent lady with progressive and modern outlook towards life.
After the tragic death of my husband 7 years ago, I decided not to work in order to make myself free to raise, care, support and guide my son, who was just 18 at the time. He is intelligent, talented, multifaceted, determined , yet humble fellow, who, after completing his medical graduation in Indian University is now desirous of pursuing his postgraduate studies in USA. He has completed two USMLE exams. Has worked in hospitals attached to University of North Carolina at Chapel Hill, for four months during Jan 13-April 13, as a Visiting Foreign Medical Graduate. He will appear for third USMLE exam in mid Sept 13 and apply for residency in US universities. He will again be in US from November 13 for the purpose of interviews to these universities.
